law.text: The Sixteenth Judicial Circuit is entitled to five (5) judges and shall have five (5) numbered divisions of the Circuit Court.
law.history: Created 2009 Ky. Acts ch. 44, sec. 1, effective August 1, 2010.

metadata.lrc-note: (8/1/2010). 2009 Ky. Acts ch. 44, sec. 1, provides that the new judgeship created by this statute shall become effective August 1, 2010.
